text: KMLY is a Regional Mexican class A radio station in Gonzales, California. ==History== KMLY went on the air on July 4, 2012, originally licensed to serve Carmel Valley, California at 105.9 FM. ==References== ==External links== * Category:2012 establishments in California Category:Mass media in Monterey County, California MLY Category:Radio stations established in 2012
title: KMLY
